properties.operhours: 9:00 am to 4:00 pm from Monday to Saturday.

Self-collect site at the Atlantic City Boat Ramp.

Vaccination service will be closed on June 23, 2021 but the UW Medicine's testing trailer will remain open.

COVID-19 Test Method:
We use a molecular RT-PCR test that detects COVID-19. It is not an antibody test. The sample is collected using a nasopharyngeal swab for adults. Different swabs are used for children that swab the front of the nasal cavity.
